<div class="card w-100 h-100">
    <div class="card-header">
        <h4>📜 Osmanlı Takvimine Göre Bugün</h4>
        <div class="card-header-action">
            <div class="badge badge-pill badge-warning">🧠 Yapay Zeka Destekli</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">

        <div class="p-4 rounded flex-grow-1"
             style="background:#fbf3dc; border:1px solid #e6d3a3;">

            <div class="text-center mb-3">
                <div class="font-weight-bold" style="font-size:18px; letter-spacing:0.5px;">
                    Padişahımızın Bugünkü Menüsü
                </div>
                <div class="text-muted" style="font-size:13px;">
                    (Saray Mutfağı – Matbah-ı Âmire)
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-3">
                <span class="badge badge-light" style="border:1px solid #e6d3a3;">
                    📅 @DateTime.Today.AddYears(-200).ToString("dd.MM.yyyy")
                </span>
                <span class="text-muted small">
                    Başaşçı Mührü: <span class="font-weight-bold">⚘</span>
                </span>
            </div>

            <div style="white-space: pre-line; line-height:1.9; font-weight:600;">
                @(ViewBag.MenuText ?? "Ferman hazırlanıyor…")
            </div>

            <div class="mt-4 d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                <div class="text-muted small">
                    “𝒮𝒶𝓇𝒶𝓎 𝒶𝒹𝒶𝒷𝒾 𝓊̈𝓏ℯ𝓇ℯ…”
                </div>
                <div class="text-right">
                    <span class="badge badge-warning" style="border:1px solid #e6d3a3;">
                        ☪ 𝒮𝒶𝓇𝒶𝓎 ℱℯ𝓇𝓂𝒶𝓃𝒾
                    </span>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-4 text-center font-italic"
                     style="color:#7a6a3a; font-size:14px;">
                    “Sende bugün padişah sofrasına buyur, bu menüyü tecrübe eyle.”
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>
